dc_description_s: This data represents Senate Districts (WI Act 94) for Wisconsin in 2023. [Legislative Districts were passed as 2023 Senate Bill 488 by the Wisconsin State Assembly and the State Senate on February 13, 2024, and then enacted by the Wisconsin Governor on Monday, February 19, 2024, as 2023 Wisconsin Act 94. Legislative district assignments of U.S. Census Blocks were appended to the 2020 U.S. Census TIGER Block geography, and then spatially dissolved by district to form the district boundaries.]
